            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes. He takes care of requests while you're too busy Synthesizing items, he's very helpful."
